{# ticket-classification-rubric.j2
   Renders a concise triage card for inclusion in CSM Slack alerts
   and Salesforce Task descriptions.
   Variables: ticket (TicketTriage output), account_name, ticket_url
#}
## Ticket Triage — #{{ ticket.id }}

**Account:** {{ account_name }}
**Summary:** {{ ticket.summary }}

| Field            | Value                       |
|------------------|-----------------------------|
| Category         | `{{ ticket.category }}`     |
| Priority         | `{{ ticket.priority | upper }}` |
| Suggested owner  | `{{ ticket.suggested_owner }}` |
| Escalate         | {{ "YES — immediate action required" if ticket.escalate else "No" }} |

{% if ticket.similar_tickets %}
**Similar tickets ({{ ticket.similar_tickets | length }}):**
{% for tid in ticket.similar_tickets %}
- #{{ tid }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if ticket.escalate %}
> **Escalation note:** This ticket meets escalation criteria.
> The assigned CSM should reach out to the customer within 1 hour.
{% endif %}

---
*Triaged by xiaoguai customer-success pack v{{ pack_version }}*
[Open ticket]({{ ticket_url }})
